{"tid":1138240,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角東食食下飯有條友比人拉左出去","createTime":"2019-05-04T11:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T11:52:14.000Z","uid":248358,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1d6e34b3d2b3764536ff196794ff56346aec1136","tid":1138240,"uid":248358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T11:49:47.000Z","msg":"頭先係旺角東某間快餐店食飯<br />\n<br />\n買野食既時候 前面個男人用八達通俾錢<br />\n<br />\n收銀話佢餘額不足<br />\n<br />\n然後佢係咁叫個收銀check下佢八達通有幾錢<br />\n收銀話冇得check<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢仲係咁叫人check 話下面買野比到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後佢話改用信用卡比 又係咁入錯密碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好啦 搞撚左勁耐<br />\n條友突然轉頭行開<br />\n佢直接放左自己銀包係櫃台<br />\n無錯 係直接放係櫃台<br />\n<br />\n跟住條友開始發癲咁係間鋪頭行黎行去<br />\n行左幾個圈仲想衝埋入經理室 <br />\n然後佢比店員阿姐阻止左<br />\n個阿姐走左出去搵差佬<br />\n<br />\n之後佢就不停係到行行企企<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DMOL5J6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDMOL5J6.png&h=92f60c4f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YNWFaaO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYNWFaaO.png&h=158b5fc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無幾耐幾個差佬入咗嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8aiXcqX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8aiXcqX.png&h=4f840ff1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n問條友做乜鳩<br />\n條友仲串串貢<br />\n有個阿Sir突然大聲喝佢<br />\n條友就縮沙<br />\n<br />\n冇幾耐條友比差佬鎖埋手扣<br />\n拉左出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614d2c5fb68e1845f949d8c9c1f935bc59fc0a92","tid":1138240,"uid":248358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T11:52:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}